OL,7,FThe mother of a man who died from a
OL,8,Fheroin overdose in Carmarthen believes
OL,9,Fher son would still be alive if drugs
OL,10,Fwere decriminalised.
OL,12,FOn 13 December 2017, Pat Hudson's life
OL,13,Fchanged forever when her son, Kevin
OL,14,FLane, fell unconscious in a locked
OL,15,Fpublic toilet following drug use and
OL,16,Fpassed away just two days after his
OL,17,F32nd birthday.
OL,19,FKevin was in recovery at the time of
OL,20,Fhis death and had begun a successful
OL,21,Fcareer as a tree surgeon.
